# Block 3 – PySpark Chicago Crime (End-to-End Data Engineering + ML)

This repository contains the full PySpark pipeline (Bronze/Silver/Gold), Spark MLlib classification models, performance optimisation evidence, and Tableau dashboard outputs for the Block 3 assignment.

## Contents
- `notebooks/` – Notebook(s) for ETL + ML workflow
- `data/` – Dataset access link (hosted externally due to size)
- `tableau/` – Public Tableau dashboard links

## Quick Links
- Notebook(s): see `notebooks/README.md`
- Dataset: see `data/README.md`
- Tableau dashboards: see `tableau/README.md`
